quran[99]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,"Alif Lam Ra. Tsino ni tsinyaali tsieshitabu nende Ikurani yinoosinjia."
  15,2,"Awundi balitsa bekomba balia bakhaya mbu, bamanyanga baba Abasalamu."
  15,3,"Baleshe sa balie ebiakhulia mana basangale, mana bakatibwe nende amekombo kobubeyi (mbu balileshelwa), ahambi ano betsa okhumanya."
  15,4,"Ne shikhwasishiakhwo olukongo lwosilwosi tawe, halali lwali nende ebise bialwo bimanyikhane."
  15,5,"Ne babulaho abandu bosibosi banyala okhuranjilila ebise biabu bieyindukho, nohomba shibanyala okhushinda tawe."
  15,6,"Ne baboola mbu; “Ewe oweshilibwa ametsulisio, toto ewe oli omulalu."
  15,7,"Shichila shina nolakhurerera Abamalaika nikali mbu ewe oli mubaboolanga obwatoto?"""
  15,8,"Efwe shikhwishinjia Abamalaika tawe halali khubwatoto (ebise biokhusishibwa khwabu nibiula), ne awo shibalihebwa obwiyangu tawe (balisishibwa butswa)."
  15,9,"Toto efwe nefwe khweshia ametsulisio kano, ne khandi toto efwe nefwe khwitsa okhukalinda."
  15,10,"Ne toto khwaruma Abarumwa mumikanda chia abandu beyimbeli."
  15,11,"Ne Omurumwa yesiyesi shiyabetselanga halali bo bamukholelanga omubayo."
  15,12,"Ne endio nilwa khuyinjisinjia mumioyo chia balia abamabii."
  15,13,"Shibaisuubilanga tawe, ne bamala okhulola shingala kali khubandu bali imbeli wabu eyo."
  15,14,"Ne khubekulilanga omuliango kwomwikulu, mana baba nibaninangamwo."
  15,15,"Bakhaboolele mbu; “Toto tsimoni tsiefu tsimeesibwe, ne efwe abeene ni ababdu khulochelwe.”"
  15,16,"Ne toto khwara mwikulu tsing’ining’ini tsikhongo, mana nikhutsirona khubalia bokhuhenga."
  15,17,"Ne khwatsilinda okhurulana nende buli Shetani ulondungwa."
  15,18,"Halali ulia uwulilisinjia mukhwiba, naye mana, amulondangakhwo nende eshichenga shiomulilo shilolokha."
  15,19,"Ne liloba khwaliala mana nikhuramwo tsingulu ne nikhumesiamwo buli eshindu khushichelo."
  15,20,"Ne nikhubakasiliamwo obulamu nende ebindi bia enywe mulabikabilanga emikabo tawe."
  15,21,"Ne shibulaho shiosishiosi halali khuli nende ebiachi biashio. Ne sikhushiishinjia tawe halali khushichelo shimanyishe."
  15,22,"Ne khureranga omuyeka kwitsulemwo liime, ne khwishinjia amatsi okhurula mumaleesi. Mana khubanywesinjia amatsi ako. Ne shimuli enywe mukabikhanga tawe."
  15,23,"Ne toto ni efwe khulamusinjia ne nefwe abafwisinjia, ne efwe nefwe abalichelama (buli eshindu)."
  15,24,"Ne toto khwamala okhumanya abaranjilila mwinywe, ne toto khwamala okhumanya abatong’a inyuma."
  15,25,"Ne toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye wakhabakhung’asie. Toto Ye niye Owamachesi, Omumanyi muno."
  15,26,"Ne toto khwalonga omundu okhurula khwiloba eliumu, eliwumukhanga (nilituywa), elirulana nende amatoyi amamali akakalukhana ifwani."
  15,27,"Ne lijini khwalilonga imbeli awo, okhurulana nende omuyeka kwomulilo."
  15,28,"Ne Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi olwa yaboolela Abamalaika mbu; “Toto esie nditsa okhulonga omundu okhurula khuliloba liwumukhanga (nilituywa), lirulana nende amatoyi amamali akakalukhana ifwani."
  15,29,"Kho olwa emala okhumulonga, mana nemufuramwo mumiuya chianje, mumurerere hasi obweni."""
  15,30,"Kho, Abamalaika boosi halala nibamurerera hasi obweni (basujuda)."
  15,31,"Halali Ibilisi, yakhaya okhuba halala nende balia bara hasi obweni (basujuda)."
  15,32,"(Nyasaye) Naboola mbu; “Ewe Ibilisi, obele orie ulabeele halala nende abarerere hasi obweni (abasujude)?”"
  15,33,"Naboola mbu; “Shenyala okhurerera hasi obweni omundu wawaloonga khuliloba eliumu, liwumukhanga (nilituywa), elirula khu matoyi amamali akakalukhana ifwani tawe.”"
  15,34,"(Nyasaye) Naboola mbu; “Mana kharula omo! Toto olondelwe muno."
  15,35,"Ne toto oli nende eshilamo shianje okhula Inyanga yeyindukho.”"
  15,36,"Naboola mbu; “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, mbelesia obwiyangu okhula inyanga yabalilamusibwa.”"
  15,37,"(Nyasaye) Naboola mbu; “Toto ewe oli mubalia bahesibwe obwiyangu."
  15,38,"Okhula inyanga yebise bimanyishe biarebwaho.”"
  15,39,"Naboola mbu; “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, shingala wukholele okhukora, toto nditsa okhubaronela (abandu) khushialo, ne toto nditsa okhubakosia boosi."
  15,40,"Halali abasumba bobo mubo abawulwa.”"
  15,41,"(Nyasaye) Naboola mbu; “Ino ni injila yokhwitsa ewanje ingololofu."
  15,42,"Ne toto ewe sholaba nende obunyali khu abasumba banje tawe, halali balia abakhulondakhwo mubalia abakora ."
  15,43,"Ne toto Jahannam niho habundu wabu wabakasilibwa boosi."
  15,44,"Ili nende emiliango saba, ne buli omuliango kuli nende ebuleka yakwakabulilwa mubo."""
  15,45,"Toto balia baria Nyasaye baliba mumikunda chiomwikulu nende tsisebele."
  15,46,"Injilemwo mushironyo, nomulembe."
  15,47,"Ne khulirusia amakhonye akali mubilifu biabu, ne baliba (shinga) abananda nibekhale khubisala biobwami nibahengana."
  15,48,"Shibulibatilakhwo obuchong’e bwosibwosi omo tawe, ne shibalirusibwamwo tawe."
  15,49,"Boolela abasumba banje mbu toto esie nesie Owobulesheli obunji, Owetsimbabaasi muno."
  15,50,"Ne mbu toto eshinyasio shianje nisho eshinyasio eshilulu muno."
  15,51,"Ne baboolele amakhuwa kabacheni ba Ibrahim."
  15,52,"Olwa benjila ewuwe nibaboola mbu; “Mulembe.” Naboola mbu: “Toto efwe khubarire.”"
  15,53,"Nibaboola mbu; “Olaria tawe. Toto efwe khukhwelesinjia akomwikhoyo, akomusiani wa obumanyi obunji.”"
  15,54,"Naboola mbu; “Oh! Mumbelesinjia akomwikhoyo kano nemalile okhukofula. Kho ni munjila shina yamumboolelangamwo akomwikhoyo kano?”"
  15,55,"Nibaboola mbu; “Toto efwe khukhuwelesinjia akomwikhoyo khubwatoto. Kho, olaba mubalia abafwitsanga omwoyo tawe.”"
  15,56,"Naboola mbu; “Ne niwina ufwitsanga omwoyo okhurulana nende tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi halali balia abakora?”"
  15,57,"Naboola mbu; “Mana shiamumbolela shindi nishina enywe Abarumwa?”"
  15,58,"Nibaboola mbu; “Toto efwe khurumilwe khubandu abamabii."
  15,59,"Halali abandu ba inzu ya Luti. Toto efwe khwitsa okhuhabina abo boosi."
  15,60,"Halali omukhasi wuwe, khumalile okhulola mbu alaba mubandu balitong’a inyuma."""
  15,61,"Mana Abarumwa olwa boola khubandu ba Luti,"
  15,62,"(Luti) naboola mbu; “Toto enywe muli abandu balamanyishe tawe.”"
  15,63,"Nibaboola mbu; “Mana efwe khukhureerere kalia kabakholelanga obukanakani."
  15,64,"Ne khukhwitsile khubulaamba, ne toto efwe khuboolanga obwatoto."
  15,65,"Kho rula nende abandu bawo ebise bieshilo muno, nawe obalondekhwo munyuma, ne yesiyesi mwinywe alakalukhanakhwo okhuhenga inyuma tawe, ne tsie wamulomesibungwa."""
  15,66,"Ne nikhumubusilia likhuwa elo, mbu emisi chiabu chitsa okhutetwa mumabwibwi."
  15,67,"Ne abandu belitokho elo nibetsa nibasangalile nibekhoya."
  15,68,"(Lut) Naboola mbu; “Toto bano ni abacheni banje, kho mulambe tsisoni tawe."
  15,69,"Ne rie Nyasaye, ne mulafimbia omurwe tawe.”"
  15,70,"Nibaboola mbu: “Efwe shikhwakhukaniakho (okhurera) abandu (belwanyi)?"""
  15,71,"Naboola mbu: “Bano nabakhana banje, (itse ebahelesie mubateshie), toto enywe nimuli abakholanga."""
  15,72,"Nditsuba khulubaka lulwo mbu: “Abo bali mubumesi bwabu, nibanyakhananga eshikhaya.”"
  15,73,"Mana eshinyasio shioluyoka nishibabukula mumabwibwi."
  15,74,"Mana nikhukhola hasi wabu okhuba hekulu. Mana nikhubakwisilia ifula yamachina keliloba lia mumulilo."
  15,75,"Toto mu ako kalimwo ameeko khubandu baretsanga amakhuwa khushichelo."
  15,76,"Ne toto tsingongo etso tsili khutsinjila tsiliwo tsiburungwakhwo."
  15,77,"Toto mu ako kalimwo ameeko khubasuubili."
  15,78,"Ne toto abandu bomushitsimi bali ababii."
  15,79,"Mana nikhubahelesia eshinyasio, ne ebialo bibili bino bili khunjila ili habulafu."
  15,80,"Ne toto Abandu ba Hijri bayingasia Abarumwa."
  15,81,"Ne nikhubahelesia ebimanyisio biefu, nabo nibalabukulamwo oluchendo tawe."
  15,82,"Ne bakwotanga tsingulu nibakasia tsinzu nomulembe."
  15,83,"Mana eshinyasio shioluyoka nishibabukula mumabwibwi."
  15,84,"Mana akabakholanga nikalabakhonyakhwo shiosishiosi tawe."
  15,85,"Ne shikhwalonga likulu nende eshialo, nende ebili hakari wabio tawe halali khubwatoto. Ne toto indukho iliula, kho leshela okhuleshela okhulayi."
  15,86,"Toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye omuloonji watoto, Omumanyi muno."
  15,87,"Ne toto khwakhwelesia tsinyaali saba tsisomungwa ebise nebise, nende Ikurani yoluyali."
  15,88,"Ne olakhosia tsimoni tsitsio khukalia akakhwahelesia emikanda chindi mubo, khandi olababelelela tawe. Ne wishilie abasuubili olubaa lulwo (lwetsimbabaasi)."
  15,89,"Ne boola mbu: “Toto esie nesie omwikanyilisi, omwinoosi owahabulafu."""
  15,90,"Shingala khweshilia balia (eshinyasio bosi) abekaba emikanda (okhwikalila obusalamu)."
  15,91,"Balia bakhola Ikurani okhuba ebitonyetonye."
  15,92,"Kho nditsuba khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi mbu, toto khulibareeba boosi."
  15,93,"Khukalia koosi akabakholanga."
  15,94,"Kho yusia akawalomesibwa, ne obe ehale nende abatsokaasi."
  15,95,"Toto efwe khukhuyela okhukhulinda okhurulana nende abakhubayilanga."
  15,96,"Balia abatsokaasinjia Nyasaye nende abanyasaye bandi, kho balitsa okhumanya."
  15,97,"Ne toto khwamanya mbu eshilifu shishio shinyoolanga obusiro khukalia akababoolanga."
  15,98,"Kho tswenula Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi khukhumwitsoomia, ne obe halala nende bamwinamilanga nibasujuda."
  15,99,"Ne olaame Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi okhuula likhuulile eliatoto elo (lifwa)."
